var e=`crossing-v1-2026-06`,t=`You let this person help with your fishing licence — fill it in and talk to AFMA about it for you. You can stop this any time.`,n=`AFMA can collect and use some of your information — your name, contact, community, and your details as a Torres Strait Islander fisher — only to look at your licence. You can see what is held about you and who looked at it, and say stop, any time.`;export{n,t as r,e as t};